{
  "stem": "27747.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After I finished the sixth grade in the tarbut in Hoszcza, I-- I went to study one year in gymnasium, and that's all we were able to-- to complete, because right then, the war started, and we came to the town of Hoszcza back.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- actually, you know, the-- the Soviets occupied at that time already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Soviets occupied the-- '39 was the war, you know, the blitzkrieg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when it was over, Poland was [INAUDIBLE] occupied by the Soviets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, of course, there was no schooling in Hebrew, and the teachers that knew the language say Polish or-- that they were of no use.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hebrew in Polish was not taught anymore in Soviet schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They established-- they called it [POLISH], which means a 10-year school program.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had-- they had Russian, and for a very brief time, Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Changed immediately to Ukrainian, and that was the two languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seventh and eighth grade I went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back in Hoszcza.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we left-- I left Rowne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, back in Hoszcza.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I told you, the house-- the homes were nationalized and so was the business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to the home moved in a Soviet citizen, Soviet citizen that were really in the government.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would say--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--we had to move out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we had to move out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we moved out into the outskirts of Hoszcza.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A farmer was renting part of his house to another Jewish family and us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time, we were only my mother, I, and my sister Leah because my sister Paula was married, and she lived in an apartment with her husband, Peter.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was librarian and he was our teacher-- my-- my teacher and my husband's teacher.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
